title: Oh Bifa Isor khaolai horw jwng
lyrics:
Oh Bifa Isor khaolai horw jwng
Swrgwni  dorkhou bekheona hw
Sudem baganao jwngbw gelegwn
Gwjwn gwjwn gwjwn, rongza mini -2
Ru ……………..Ru ……………….
(A)
Gwsw mwdwm hwna dinwi
Swr sibiyw nwngkhou -2
Raobw gwiya buhumao subunga -2
(B)
Janw hagwu papi jwng dinwi
Arose dwnw oblabw -2
Nima ha hwnangwn jwngkhou -2
